title: Edward Hopper 2024 Wall Calendar
description:
Realist American painter, Edward Hopper, portrayed images of life and quiet solitude. This colorful 12 month calendar includes some of his best works.

  • Dimensions: 12 x 12 in.
  • Includes major international holidays, lunar phases, and zodiac signs
  • Features 7 languages: Italian, English, German, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Japanese
